                               Presents



                       Mass Effect - US TO GERMAN Conversion Patch
                          

                               
                               Notes:    
  
                    
           With great help from Beatpirate, munition, Revan and speznaz
           we proudly present a German Conversion Patch for the US Version      
           of Mass Effect for PC. 

           No new Crack is needed now.
                      
           Just use MASS.EFFECT.CRACKFiX.READ.NFO-iND and this Patch on  
           the US Version from this Game.
 
           Now you can play fully German Localised without needing a new        
           Crack for the EU-MULTI5 Version of the Game.




                             Greetz goes to                    
 
               Gniarf (for fixing the Crack from Reloaded)
               eddd (for implementing the Crack into the exe)
               Revan (for making the nfo of the Crack) 
               Beatpirate (for providing the initial German Language Files)
               munitio (for the providing the missing German Language Files)
               speznaz (for testing)     

               and of course RELOADED (you are a milestone in the scene)
